statements: SELECT * FROM quantum_evolution;
SELECT state_id, state_description FROM quantum_evolution ORDER BY time_stamp DESC;

SELECT state_id, state_description, time_stamp FROM quantum_evolution WHERE state_description ILIKE '%quantum%';

SELECT state_name, measurement_value FROM quantum_states JOIN state_measurements ON quantum_states.id = state_measurements.state_id WHERE measurement_time > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY measurement_value DESC;

SELECT state_name, measurement_value, measurement_time FROM quantum_states JOIN state_measurements ON quantum_states.id = state_measurements.state_id WHERE measurement_value < 0.5 GROUP BY state_name HAVING COUNT(state_name) > 1;
